

==================================

Remove Folders from Dir

==================================

Go to the file below 

~/ .config/user-dirs.dirs

and comment out the dir you dont wish to have show up 

Then go to the below via sudo 

/etc/xdg/user-dirs.defaults

and comment out the shortcuts you dont want

----- but probably the easiest way is to rename the folders to .dirs/ so they are hidden!



